<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1928-03-02T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1928-03-02T13:00:00-05:00" n="292" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d292">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">881.00/1380: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Herrick</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-03-02T18:00:00+00:00"><hi rend="italic">March 2,
                                        1928—6 p.m.</hi></date><lb/>[Received March 2—5:17
                                p.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>56. Madrid’s telegram of February 21, 6 p.m. to the Department. Foreign
                            Office informally advises me that agreement concluding Franco-Spanish
                            Tangier negotiations will probably be signed by Briand and Spanish
                            Ambassador before former leaves for Geneva which means tomorrow. Main
                            points of agreement appear to be: <list>
                                <label>1.</label>
                                <item>Reforms of a judicial nature.</item>
                                <label>2.</label>
                                <item>Spanish Commander of Police, and,</item>
                                <label>3.</label>
                                <item>Spanish Inspector of Police responsible to international
                                    authorities.</item>
                            </list></p>
                        <p>Repeated to London, Rome, Madrid, Tangier.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Herrick</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>